* 61302 VTI STANDARD SCRIPT 302
* OCTOBER 18, 2010
* -----------------------------------
* INITIALIZE TEMP CHAMBER
* -----------------------------------
TC I 2
TC T 25 900 	SET TEMP, WAIT
* -----------------------------------
* INITIALIZE BAROMETERS
* -----------------------------------
BA E 0 3               ESCAPE
BA C CMD900 2801, 0 5  SET CAL MODE
BA C CMD920, 0 5       ERASE CAL DATA
BA C CMD955, 0 3       RESET INTERNAL OFFSET
BA C CMD960 2, 0 3     USE INTERNAL OFFSET
BA C CMD110 4, 0 3     RAW MODE
BA C CMD120 10000, 0 3 MULT
BA C CMD125 0, 0 3     OFFSET
BA C CMD105 10, 0 3    SET TO 10 SAMPLE AVG
BA C CMD420, 0 3       STORE PARAMETERS
BA C CMD300 2, 0 3     OPERATE
*
* -----------------------------------
* CYCLE TEMP AND PRESSURE
* -----------------------------------
* CYCLE 1
TC T 65 3600 SET TEMP, WAIT
GOSUB CYCLEPRESS
TC T 0 3600  SET TEMP, WAIT
GOSUB CYCLEPRESS
TC T -50 3600 SET TEMP, WAIT
GOSUB CYCLEPRESS
TC T 0 3600  SET TEMP, WAIT
GOSUB CYCLEPRESS
*
