* GOSUB CYCLEPRESS
*
*
TC T 25 1800  SET TEMP, WAIT
*
* -----------------------------------
* INITIALIZE BAROMETERS
* -----------------------------------
PC I 3	              INITIALIZE PRESSURE CONTROLLER
PC P 850 300   	      SET PRESSURE, WAIT 5 MIN 
BA E 0 2              ESCAPE
BA C CMD110 4, 0 2    RAW MODE
BA C CMD900 2801, 0 5 SET CAL MODE
BA C CMD300 2, 0 30   OPERATE, WAIT 30 SEC FOR AVG PRESSURE WITHOUT OFFSET
BA C CMD950 1, 0 5    SET INTERNAL OFFSET AT 850 USING AvgRawP
BA C CMD420, 0 5      STORE PARAMETERS
*
PC S                  STOP PRESSURE
*
* -----------------------------------
* START CALIBRATION
* -----------------------------------
* 
