* ------------------------------
*
TC T 25 1800  	   SET TEMP, WAIT
BA E 0 3           ESCAPE
BA C CMD900 0, 0 3 CAL ENABLE OFF
BA C CMD110 1, 0 3 OUTPUT FORMAT ASCII
BA C CMD420, 0 5   STORE SETTINGS
BA C CMD300 2, 0 3 RUN
*
* ------------------------------
* START CALIBRATION CHECK
* ------------------------------
*
TC T -40 3600 	SET TEMP, WAIT
GOSUB CHKPRESS
TC T -25 1800 	SET TEMP, WAIT
GOSUB CHKPRESS
TC T 0 1800 	SET TEMP, WAIT 
GOSUB CHKPRESS
TC T 25 1800 	SET TEMP, WAIT 
GOSUB CHKPRESS
TC T 60 1800 	SET TEMP, WAIT 
GOSUB CHKPRESS
*
TC T 25 1800 	SET TEMP, WAIT
*
* BA C CMD900 2801, 0 2  CAL ENABLE
* BA C CMD955, 0 2       CLEAR INTERNAL OFFSET
* PC P 850 60  	         SET PRESSURE, WAIT
* BA C CMD950 2, 0 5     SET INTERNAL OFFSET USING FinalPressure
* BA C CMD420, 0 2       STORE PARAMETERS
* BA C CMD900 0, 0 2     CAL ENABLE OFF
*
TC S
PC S
ST
